rioritize self-care activities such as exercise and spending time with loved ones.\n\nFeedback and Support: The facilitator provided feedback and encouragement to Emily and the rest of the group, emphasizing the importance of self-care and seeking support when needed. Participants were encouraged to continue practicing the techniques discussed in the session and to reach out to each other for support.\n\nFollow-Up Plan:\nEmily expressed interest in attending future sessions of the Calm Minds Stress Management Group. The facilitator provided information about upcoming sessions and encouraged Emily to continue practicing the coping strategies discussed today. Emily agreed to keep a journal to track her progress and reflect on her experiences with managing stress."
